    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸在手绘风格的银河恶魔城游戏《超级罗博伊》的世界中！</strong> <br>在一个后末日世界中，扮演一位寻找父亲的小机器人，展开一段充满情感的冒险旅程。探索互相连接的地图，对抗突变体与机械敌人，并从他们身上学习全新的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras/c4364cef0bb071205b80b5ef4f51ea41.avif?t=1765786165\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras_big/c4364cef0bb071205b80b5ef4f51ea41.avif?t=1765786165 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>学习敌人的技能</strong> <br>击败敌人，获取多种技能，包括移动强化与强力新武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras/73eed4da025b8be2cec3ce1fda4764ae.avif?t=1765786165\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras_big/73eed4da025b8be2cec3ce1fda4764ae.avif?t=1765786165 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>自由探索</strong> <br>在充满科幻元素的末日世界中自由探索，脱离主线路径还能发现隐藏奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras/79f4caa58f0f3eb8f2c8457d8ed5d9a4.avif?t=1765786165\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras_big/79f4caa58f0f3eb8f2c8457d8ed5d9a4.avif?t=1765786165 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>揭示罗博伊的过去</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验一段感人至深的故事，灵感来自但丁的《神曲》与经典科幻小说，通过漫画式过场呈现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>利用敌人的弱点</strong> <br>掌握元素攻击、造成状态异常，并学习独特招式，对强敌造成毁灭性打击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras/a3831a3883817cbb8bc7b3cc1b2351b4.avif?t=1765786165\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras_big/a3831a3883817cbb8bc7b3cc1b2351b4.avif?t=1765786165 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>挑战手绘风格的强大Boss</strong> <br>面对各具特色的Boss战，全手绘设计的视觉风格为《超级罗博伊》的世界注入生命，考验你的战斗技巧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras/f2c7cb650712778f27df5f667ae0cdbb.avif?t=1765786165\" width=774 height=434 /></span></p>",
